OL,3,C'One in four councils could lose
OL,4,Cmoney' under Government's funding
OL,5,Cproposals
OL,7,FAround a quarter of councils in
OL,8,FEngland could lose money under the
OL,9,FGovernment's proposed reforms to how
OL,10,Flocal authorities are funded, analysis
OL,11,Fhas found.
OL,13,FA report from the Institute for Fiscal
OL,14,FStudies (IFS) said the changes would
OL,15,Fcreate big "winners and losers" as
OL,16,Fministers attempt to address perceived
OL,17,Funfairness in levels of core funding
OL,18,Facross the country.
