OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer's own council, Camden
OL,8,Fin north London, will be hit by the
OL,9,Freforms when taking inflation into
OL,10,Faccount, the IFS added.
OL,12,FThe think tank said Camden, along with
OL,13,Fother inner London boroughs including
OL,14,FWestminster, will have less money to
OL,15,Fspend on services even if they
OL,16,Fincrease council tax by the maximum
OL,17,Famount allowed.
