OL,7,FThe changes, which will come into
OL,8,Feffect from next year, are being
OL,9,Fconsulted on by ministers.
OL,11,FThe Government plans to create a new
OL,12,Fmethodology to assess local authority
OL,13,Fneeds relatively and factor in
OL,14,Fpopulation and deprivation. It will
OL,15,Falso assess need for adult and
OL,16,Fchildren's services.
