OL,7,FOverall spending will fall for 186
OL,8,Fcouncils and rise by the same total
OL,9,Fsum for 161. One in 10 will see a fall
OL,10,Fin overall funding, while one in 10
OL,11,Fwill see an increase of 10% or more.
OL,13,FThe overall Government spend on local
OL,14,Fauthorities will not change. The
OL,15,Fchanges will be phased in across three
OL,16,Fyears, from 2026/27 to 2028/29.
