OL,7,FKate Ogden, co-author of the IFS
OL,8,Freport and a senior research economist
OL,9,Fwith the think tank, said: "England
OL,10,Fhas lacked a rational system of local
OL,11,Fgovernment funding for at least 12
OL,12,Fyears ` and arguably more like 20. It
OL,13,Fis therefore welcome that the nettle
OL,14,Fof funding reform is being grasped,
OL,15,Fand some councils will benefit
OL,16,Fsubstantially under the new system.
