OL,7,FThe report added: "It is somewhat
OL,8,Fsurprising that, on average, councils
OL,9,Fin the most deprived 30% of areas
OL,10,Fwould see very similar changes in
OL,11,Foverall funding over the next three
OL,12,Fyears to those for councils in the
OL,13,Fmiddle 40% of areas."
OL,15,FIt noted that rural areas, which
OL,16,Ffeared being badly hit by changes,
OL,17,Fwill benefit from a "remoteness
OL,18,Fadjustment" which will compensate
OL,19,Fareas with higher needs due to being
OL,20,Ffar from large towns.
