OL,7,FLondon will gain the least, with a
OL,8,Fcash-terms increase in funding of 8%
OL,9,Fin the next three years. Analysis by
OL,10,Fthe London Councils collective has
OL,11,Fhighlighted the risk of the funding
OL,12,F"dramatically underestimating" needs
OL,13,Ffor local services in parts of the
OL,14,Fcapital.
OL,16,FIt noted the city has the highest rate
OL,17,Fof poverty in the country when housing
OL,18,Fcosts are factored in.
