OL,7,FOutside the capital, the East Midlands
OL,8,F(22%) and Yorkshire & the Humber (19%)
OL,9,Fare set to see the biggest increases
OL,10,Fin funding, with the South East set to
OL,11,Fsee the smallest at 13%.
