OL,7,FMs Ogden added: "The Government should
OL,8,Fconsider giving highly affected
OL,9,Fcouncils which currently have low
OL,10,Fcouncil tax rates greater flexibility
OL,11,Fto bring their council tax bills up to
OL,12,Fmore typical levels to offset funding
OL,13,Flosses.
OL,15,F"More generally, reform of council
OL,16,Ffunding allocations is just one part
OL,17,Fof the financial sustainability
OL,18,Fpuzzle. Efforts to reduce demands on,
OL,19,Fand the cost of providing, local
OL,20,Fservices through reform and the use of
OL,21,Fnew technology will also be vital."
